      <!-- Article Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <h2 id="what-is-proprofs">What is ProProfs Chat?</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-gray-200 p-8 mb-8">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-800 mb-6">ProProfs Chat is a comprehensive live chat software solution designed for businesses of all sizes, from small startups to large enterprises. Launched in 2005 by ProProfs, the platform has evolved into a feature-rich customer communication tool that combines traditional live chat with modern AI capabilities, serving over 1 million users worldwide.</p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">🏢 Company Background</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>• <strong>Founded:</strong> 2005 (19+ years in business)</li>
                <li>• <strong>Headquarters:</strong> Los Angeles, California</li>
                <li>• <strong>Global Reach:</strong> 100+ countries</li>
                <li>• <strong>Customer Base:</strong> 1M+ active users</li>
                <li>• <strong>Industry Focus:</strong> Education, Healthcare, E-commerce, SaaS</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">🎯 Core Positioning</h4>
              <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li>• <strong>Target Market:</strong> SMBs to Enterprise</li>
                <li>• <strong>Primary Use Case:</strong> Customer support & sales</li>
                <li>• <strong>Key Differentiator:</strong> Affordable enterprise features</li>
                <li>• <strong>Deployment:</strong> Cloud-based SaaS</li>
                <li>• <strong>Integration:</strong> 40+ third-party platforms</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Unlike pure AI chatbots like ChatGPT or Claude, ProProfs Chat is a <strong>hybrid live chat platform</strong> that combines human agents with AI automation. This makes it particularly valuable for businesses that need the personal touch of human interaction while benefiting from AI efficiency for routine tasks.</p>

        <h2 id="key-features">Key Features & Capabilities</h2>

        <h3>Core Live Chat Features</h3>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              Real-Time Messaging
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>• Instant message delivery and notifications</li>
              <li>• Typing indicators and read receipts</li>
              <li>• File sharing (documents, images, videos)</li>
              <li>• Emoji and rich text formatting</li>
              <li>• Message history and conversation logs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
              Multi-Agent Support
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>• Unlimited agent accounts</li>
              <li>• Department-based routing</li>
              <li>• Agent availability status</li>
              <li>• Workload distribution</li>
              <li>• Supervisor monitoring and intervention</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
