        <h2 id="ai-features">AI-Powered Features in ProProfs Chat</h2>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 border border-purple-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">🤖 AI & Automation Capabilities</h3>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-4">🧠 Smart Automation</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-purple-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• <strong>Auto-Responders:</strong> Instant replies to common questions</li>
                <li>• <strong>Chatbot Integration:</strong> AI handles routine inquiries</li>
                <li>• <strong>Smart Routing:</strong> AI-powered visitor-to-agent matching</li>
                <li>• <strong>Predictive Typing:</strong> Suggested responses for agents</li>
                <li>• <strong>Intent Recognition:</strong> Understands visitor goals</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-4">📈 Intelligent Analytics</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm text-purple-700 space-y-2">
                <li>• <strong>Sentiment Analysis:</strong> Detects customer emotions</li>
                <li>• <strong>Conversation Insights:</strong> AI-powered conversation analysis</li>
                <li>• <strong>Performance Predictions:</strong> Forecasts peak times</li>
                <li>• <strong>Automated Reports:</strong> AI-generated performance summaries</li>
                <li>• <strong>Trend Detection:</strong> Identifies emerging customer issues</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-purple-200">
            <p class="text-purple-800 text-center"><strong>💡 AI Integration Note:</strong> While ProProfs Chat includes AI features, it's primarily a human-agent platform enhanced by AI, not a pure AI chatbot like ChatGPT or Claude.</p>
          </div>
